    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivering power through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the legendary MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry performs as intended. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A true driver\u2019s specification for those who value mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
